txt.en: The strange woman can be found back at her cabin.\n\nYou should bring the meat to the strange woman.
Bats and crawlers can be found in Rath Dúath.\n\nThe strange woman has asked you to gather meat from bats and crawlers.
Bring the troubling meats to the strange woman

You greet the woman and ask for her name. She does not answer your question, nor does she look you in the eye when she finally speaks.\n\n‘My family becomes more famished with every day that passes. The meat of the bats and crawlers of this land could sustain us. Wilt thou help us stave off hunger a while longer?’
You uncertainly hand the woman the troubling meats for which she asked.\n\n‘Thou hast done what thou must. When thy task is finished, wilt thou also aid my child?’
A nameless woman requires food to feed her family in the harsh land of the Morgul Vale.
